Description:
You arrive at some ruins where you find a large stone shelf with books that look really old, there are also several remains of books and scrolls scattered everywhere so you deduce that this was a great library in ancient times.

Most of the books turn to dust just by touching them and the ones that are left you don't know how to read them or they are missing pieces.

After searching for a while you only find a large history book, a few scrolls and a book that talks about electricity and ancient technology.
DescriptionAction: This last book could be just what the gnome was looking for...
